{
  "text": "For a given initial condition, theoretically estimating the minimal time for controllability towards \u03b8 and corresponding controls is an open problem in our semilinear setting, since spectral estimates specific to the linear case (used in [CITATION_1] ) are not available.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "53075251"
